Description: Network monitoring tool for Raspberry Pi
 Netpulse is a lightweight network monitoring tool designed for Raspberry Pi.
 It measures bandwidth and latency using librespeed-cli and provides a
 responsive web interface with charts and statistics.
 .
 Features:
 - Automatic network measurements
 - SQLite database for data storage
 - Responsive web interface with Bootstrap
 - Systemd timer for reliable measurements
 - Easy DEB package installation
